OL,4,CCustomers fed up with Covid excuse for
OL,5,Cbad service
OL,6, Customers are fed up with being told
OL,7, they are getting poor service "because
OL,8, of Covid", according to research.
OL,10,FFirms are being accused of using the
OL,11,Fpandemic as an excuse for long waits on
OL,12,Fthe telephone or late deliveries, the
OL,13,FUK Institute of Customer Service said.
OL,15,FIt said that consumers were initially
OL,16,Ftolerant of delays and other issues as
OL,17,Fbusinesses fought to cope with the
OL,18,Feffects of the crisis.
OL,20,FBut it said a blanket excuse was no
OL,21,Flonger sufficient.
